==English==
===Etymology===
From ''[[annul]]'' + ''[[-ment]]''

===Noun===
'''annulment'''
# The act of [[annul]]ling; [[abolition]]; [[nullification]]; [[cancellation]].
# [[Invalidation]]; [[declaration]] of something as being [[invalid]], especially of a [[marriage]] or [[legal]] [[contract]].
# Total [[destruction]].

